<lb n="3"/>Ātittampūtiyeṉ piramateyam Īcāṉamaṅkalattu
<lb n="4" break="no"/>t tirucceṉtuṟaik kaṟṟaḷipparame<hi rend="grantha">śva</hi> ra<supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied>kku Uraiyūrkū
